----[1 write permission 
Give the permission to write the "include" directory to the web server.



----[2 installation process
- Go to http://www.yourdomain.com/path/admin.php3
- Setup the newsletter


----[3 Newsletter Admin Area
- Go to http://www.yourdomain.com/path/admin.php3
- Fill the field with your password (set in during the installation process)
- Enjoy!


